<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你最近有没有计划去找<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实，<delay8 />
我向<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />借了样东西，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但一直没有机会去还<tag a="110" b="0" />
