	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">可以！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />抱歉</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前<delay20 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />来玩的时候，<delay20 />
有东西落在我家了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是能立马察觉就好了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我是等那家伙离开一段时间以后才发现的。<pageBreak />我本来打算亲自送过去，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />却正好碰上一堆琐事缠身，<delay8 />
一直没有能抽出时间来。<pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我一直想着这件事情，<delay20 />
不还回去我就放心不下<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />我帮你送过去吧？</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />确实很不放心啊</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了对了，<delay20 />你听我说啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近，<delay8 />有一个<delay8 /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的包裹
送错到我家来了。
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我差点就准备打开了，
还好及时发现，<delay8 />没有酿成大错！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总感觉我去送有点尴尬<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以，不好意思！<delay8 />
你愿意帮我把包裹<delay20 />
送去给<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">知道了！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />抱歉</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢啦！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
