<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那这个<delay20 />就拜托你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的吗？！<delay20 />太感谢你了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是这个东西，<delay8 />
麻烦你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
