<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我会努力<delay8 />搞定的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说得也是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
