<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我感觉我有一点勇气了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">这种事自然是尽早好。<delay20 />
