<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总之拜托你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我上次拜托你送还的东西<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
